Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user

Class Faculty

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.User
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.Faculty
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Faculty>
public class Faculty extends User implements Comparable<Faculty>
A class representing a Faculty. Stores information about a Faculty, including first name, last name, id, email, hashed password, and max classes.
Author:
Brendon Hablutzel, Parker Morrison
